                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8490" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">TM-0026</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1607 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数智之石，可以攻玉：数字赋能太平湖生态产品价值实现之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Polishing Stone of Digital Wisdom: Pathways to Unleashing the Value of Ecological Products in Taiping Lake through Digital Empowerment</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吕宛青，肖钊富，毛晓漫，陈飚，陈伟，吕达非</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南太平湖投资开发有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化、体育和娱乐业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字赋能；生态产品价值实现；数字生态；新质生产力；太平湖森林小镇；2025百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Digital empowerment; Realizing the value of ecological products; Digital ecosystem; New quality productivity; Taiping Lake Forest Town</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字经济背景下如何创新实现生态产品价值成为理论和实践关注的重点。本案例以太平湖森林小镇的数智化转型为主线，详细阐述了该地区在太平湖投资开发有限责任公司的引领下，如何从严重的石漠化区域蝶变为生态旅游热点的过程。公司在治理石漠化的基础上逐步尝试开发生态产品并打造景区，但在建设过程中遭遇了多重挑战，通过集思广益，抢抓机遇，最终确定了数智化转型的道路。公司利用数字技术对小镇的生态农业、园区管理、旅游服务和市场营销等方面进行赋能，推动生态产品转变为生态资本从而有效实现了生态产品价值。本案例旨在引导学生辨明数字赋能生态产品价值实现的动因及过程，激发学生对数智技术利用和新质生产力实践的探索性思考，为创新景区管理和推动地区高质量发展提供了一定的借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">How to innovate and realize the value of ecological products in the context of the digital economy has become a focal point of both theoretical and practical concerns. This case study, centered on the digital transformation of the Forest Town in Taiping Lake, delves into the transformation of the region, which, under the guidance of Taiping Lake Investment and Development Co., Ltd., has successfully transitioned from a severely eroded area to a popular ecotourism destination. The company, while addressing desertification, gradually ventured into developing ecological products and constructing a tourist destination. However, it faced numerous challenges during the construction phase. Through collective brainstorming and seizing opportunities, the company ultimately decided on a digital transformation path. Employing digital technology, the company enhanced the ecological agriculture, park management, tourism services, and marketing in the town, facilitating the transformation of ecological products into ecological capital, thus effectively realizing their value. This case study aims to guide students in identifying the drivers and processes behind the realization of ecological product value through digital empowerment. It seeks to inspire students to explore the utilization of digital intelligence technologies and the practice of new productivity, providing valuable insights for innovative scenic area management and promoting high-quality regional development.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《旅游景区经营与管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生态产品的概念内涵；动态能力理论；数字赋能概念；数字化转型理论；生态产品价值实现理论；新质生产力的概念内涵</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-08</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
